<item>
            <title>[SPARK-7669] Builds against Hadoop 2.6+ get inconsistent curator dependencies</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-7669</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you build spark against Hadoop 2.6 you end up with an inconsistent set of curator dependencies -curator-recipe 2.4.0 with curator 2.6.0.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A dedicated hadoop-2.6 profile along with extraction of curator version into a property can keep the curator versions in sync, along with ZK.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Hadoop 2.6&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12830190">SPARK-7669</key>
